{"id":278,"date":"2017-07-25T17:45:42","date_gmt":"2017-07-25T17:45:42","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/hoodbuilder.dev\/?page_id=278"},"modified":"2023-10-28T12:24:15","modified_gmt":"2023-10-28T12:24:15","slug":"range-guard","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/fire-suppression-systems\/range-guard\/","title":{"rendered":"Range Guard"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1500556319702{background-color: #eeeeec !important;}&#8221;][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-2 vc_col-lg-8 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-10&#8243;]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e556e67820\" data-id=\"685e556e67820\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"big-para-blue\">For over 25 years, we have been providing businesses like yours with range guard fire suppression systems that are reliable and cost-effective. We provide and install all the equipment, and even provide follow-ups to ensure that your equipment comes into action when you need it most.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e556e67835\" data-id=\"685e556e67835\" data-height=\"60\" data-height-mobile=\"40\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"40\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e556e67842\" data-id=\"685e556e67842\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-7 vc_col-md-7&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2>Range Guard Fire Suppression Systems<\/h2>\n<p>Even if you take all the precautions, fire can wreak havoc on your commercial kitchen space. Your property can become damaged, your staff or customers injured, and there could even be loss of life.<\/p>\n<p>Many commercial kitchens make use of wet chemical fire suppression systems, but these can leave a soggy mess, not to mention many of them contain corrosive materials that can be almost as damaging as the fire itself.<\/p>\n<p>To prevent fires and stop them when they occur, we recommend a range guard fire suppression system.<\/p>\n<h2>About Range Guard Systems<\/h2>\n<p>The Range Guard fire suppression system is a pre-engineered solution, which protects the heating equipment and cooking appliances against fires. It has a unique design for extended coverage and uses a wet chemical agent which has a high potential for putting out flames before it spreads. The entire process of turning burning fats and oils into soap to stop the fire and prevent reignition is termed saponification. The soap can be easily washed away later.<\/p>\n<p>You can always rely on Hood Builder to outfit your commercial kitchen with a highly powerful fire prevention system.<\/p>\n<p>Our in-depth knowledge and unmatched expertise allow us to install a fire protection system based on the specific needs of a commercial kitchen or restaurant. We have been operating in this sector for more than 25 years and have earned the trust of a range of clients due to our hard work and the highest quality of standards. Our fire extinguishing solutions are both reliable and budget-friendly. Our professionals are expertly trained in the installation and maintenance of the Range Guard kitchen fire suppression system.<\/p>\n<h2>Other Range Guard Features<\/h2>\n<p>At Hood Builder, we provide you with the most options to keep your restaurant running effectively, without the threat of fire destroying all your hard work.<\/p>\n<p>All our range guards come with the following features:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Flexible pipe configurations<\/li>\n<li>Factory-filled pressure cylinders<\/li>\n<li>Smaller nozzles with foil bursting discs to prevent blockage<\/li>\n<li>Nozzle swivel adaptors<\/li>\n<li>Valves with pressure gauges for easy-to-see status indication<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Don\u2019t allow a fire to break out in your kitchen. Call Hood Builder today and ask about a range guard fire suppression system.<\/p>\n<p><strong>For a full and fast price quote, contact Hood Builder today at (800) 750-7055.<\/strong>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-1 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-4&#8243;][vc_wp_custommenu nav_menu=&#8221;14&#8243; el_class=&#8221;wps-sidebar-related-links&#8221; title=&#8221;Related Links&#8221;]<div class=\"templatera_shortcode\"><div id=\"\" class=\"wps-row-container vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" ><div class=\"container wps-vc-container\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"\/services\/restaurant-services\/\" title=\"Restaurant Services\">\n\n            <div id=\"wps-sidebar-btn-105129\" class=\"sidebar-widget-button-details\">\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button-text\">\n                    <p>Restaurant Services<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-arrow\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/themes\/wps-hoodbuilder\/assets\/images\/icon-arrow-sidebar-services.svg\" alt=\"\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/fire-suppression-systems\/\" title=\"Fire Protection\">\n\n            <div id=\"wps-sidebar-btn-559332\" class=\"sidebar-widget-button-details\">\n 